text: Wykeham, Lincolnshire may refer to several deserted villages in Lincolnshire, UK: *East Wykeham, Ludford, Lincolnshire, in the civil parish of Ludford *West Wykeham, Ludford, Lincolnshire, in the civil parish of Ludford *Wykeham, Nettleton, Lincolnshire, near Nettleton Top, Nettleton *Wykeham, Weston, Lincolnshire, in the civil parish of Weston
title: Wykeham, Lincolnshire
